'''''The Lord of the Rings Online: Corsairs of Umbar''''' ('''Update 38''') is the tenth expansion for ''[[The Lord of the Rings Online]]''.

In this expansion, which is set after the [[War of the Ring]], [[Aragorn|King Elessar]] and [[Arwen|Queen Arwen]] traverse the kingdom of Gondor following the Free Peoples' victory in the War of the Ring. Yet, order is threatened by the emergence of a dangerous force across the [[Bay of Belfalas]]. The rise of the Kindred of the Coins casts a shadow over [[Umbar]], the City of the [[Corsairs]], as this faction tightens its grip on power and trouble looms.

==Updates==
===Update 39: Arenas of Conflict===
''Arenas of Conflict'' was released on [[13 March]], [[2024]].
* Multiple instances were added in [[Umbar]]: three dungeons and a raid.

===Update 40: Beneath the Surface===
''Beneath the Surface'' was released on [[15 May]], [[2024]].
* Opened five new areas of Umbar-môkh, the Neaths beneath Umbar Baharbêl, city of [[Corsairs]]
* Added Chapter 9 of "The Song of Waves and Wind"

===Update 41: On the Wing===
''On the Wing'' was released on [[31 July]], [[2024]].
* Addition of a new hobby: Birding
* Significant re-vamp of the Loremaster class
